        Smooch integration
      </h2>

      <p class="lead">Link Dialog to your <a href="https://smooch.io">Smooch</a> account and messages going through the smooch platform will be ingested automatically.</p>


      <h3 class="page-header">How to install</h3>

      <p>The installation does not require any development time and can be added by simply clicking through the install steps, which take 2 minutes to complete.</p>

      <p>1. Login to your Dialog account and go to your bot's Integrations.</p>

      <p>2. Select ‘Configure’ on the Smooch option.</p>

      <p>3. Select ‘Link Dialog to Smooch’</p>

      <p>4. This will open Smooch in a new tab and ask you to authorize the application. Authorizing Dialog will enable Dialog to receive webhooks from Smooch when a message is created.</p>


